<D>__{nah, coppers don't do nothing, do they.}
<C>__{ed}
<D>__{those streets up in the hills, man. gotta be real careful, keep your eye on the ball. two o'clock in the morning, it's dark, your mind is all agitated, you're drivin' a little too fast ...}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{those curves don't kid around.}
<A>__{could be talking about the girl. wilson doesn't move. but touch him, he'll explode. out the window lights are passing, but no landmarks. he might as well be on the moon.}
